  <prompt>
    The project's CLAUDE.md (this file: projects/spaarke-auth-v2-and-hardening/CLAUDE.md) already contains a "🚨 ACTIVE AUTH V2 REFACTOR — DO NOT REGRESS" section that lists MUST NOT and MUST rules. This is the highest-enforcement surface because project CLAUDE.md is auto-loaded every Claude Code session in this worktree.

    Verify the prohibition section is correct and complete. Cross-check against the audit doc §8.2 Layer 3 (project CLAUDE.md prohibition specification). If any items are missing or wrong, fix them.

    Specifically verify:
    - All MUST NOT items from §8.2 Layer 3 are present
    - All MUST items from §8.2 Layer 3 are present
    - References to DEPRECATED-* filenames match the actual files (from task 001)
    - Reference to the audit doc path is correct
    - "When in doubt" escalation guidance is present
  </prompt>
  <role>Senior engineer verifying agent-enforcement surface. Precision matters; this file is loaded by every agent session.</role>
  <goal>
    Project CLAUDE.md prohibition section accurately captures all MUST/MUST NOT rules from audit §8.2 Layer 3. No discrepancies between this file and the canonical audit doc.
  </goal>
  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/AUDIT-FINDINGS-AUTH-SYSTEM.md §8.2 Layer 3 (the spec for this prohibition)</file>
      <file>projects/spaarke-auth-v2-and-hardening/CLAUDE.md (the file to verify)</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>
  <steps>
    <step>Read .claude/AUDIT-FINDINGS-AUTH-SYSTEM.md §8.2 Layer 3 — note every MUST NOT and MUST bullet listed.</step>
    <step>Read projects/spaarke-auth-v2-and-hardening/CLAUDE.md — find the "🚨 ACTIVE AUTH V2 REFACTOR — DO NOT REGRESS" section.</step>
    <step>Cross-check: every bullet in §8.2 Layer 3 must appear in CLAUDE.md. Note discrepancies.</step>
    <step>If discrepancies exist, edit CLAUDE.md to add missing items or fix wording. If no discrepancies, mark task complete.</step>
    <step>Verify the DEPRECATED-* file references in CLAUDE.md match actual filenames from task 001.</step>
    <step>Verify the path to AUDIT-FINDINGS-AUTH-SYSTEM.md is relative and resolves correctly.</step>
    <step>If edits were made, commit with message: "docs(auth): align project CLAUDE.md prohibition with audit §8.2 (PF-11)" + standard footer.</step>
  </steps>
  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion>Every MUST NOT bullet from audit §8.2 Layer 3 appears in project CLAUDE.md prohibition section.</criterion>
    <criterion>Every MUST bullet from audit §8.2 Layer 3 appears in project CLAUDE.md.</criterion>
